ook soo where do i start!!! this weekend has been AMAZING!!!no really its the best weekend of my life.. and i think yesterday we my best birthday ever!!!!

    Thursday was fun.. more presents.. lots of food (two dinners) and pie.. and playin Madden 2005 with my cousins and getting my ass kicked!! i admited my defeat when it was 74-0.. yea.. i suck!!! so it was alot of fun to see my cousion cause i never see them..
    so FRIDAY!!!! YAY my birthday!!! YAY.. it was AWSOME!! so i wake up at..umm... 10:30ish.. and my phone rings.. and guess who??? it was dan... i was like half alseep... it was funny.. so he goes.. what are u doing tonight?? and i was like nothing.. (ok i lied i had plans to go out with my family.. to the movies.. but if he wanted to do somthing i was soo gonna cancle any plans) and he was like do u want to go bowling and then watch a movies.. i was like that would be fun.. so the entire day i couldnt stop smiling.. u know how that is.. it was funny.. so me kell .dan and Brandon.. all went to dans house.. and tryed to watch Oceans 11 (i love that movie) when i say try i mean we were to busy fighting with each other and throwing pillows... haha.. it was fun.. Brandon is soooo funny.. and him and kell were sooo freeking cute.. they were holding hands with cuddleing.. it was cute.. soo im just sitting next to dan watching the movie.. and then he grabs my hand!! i was soo shocked... :)so u know we were watching the movie and holdin hands and cuddling.. it was really really cute.. i like that kid soo much .. it really weird i dont know how to explian. it.. but theres just somthing about him that makes him soo different and sooo perfect... after the movie and some pillow fighting and name calling.. and giving brandon the finger like 20 times!!! we went bowling..
    that was fun.. i decided that i totally suck.,.. Dan got like 4 stricks in one game... and i got like a 20over all .. ya im really bad.. but i was kinda tired to.. soo ..ill blame it on that.. but when we were paying for the lane he wouldnt let me pay!!!!! he's like its not ethical!! i was like aww no ill really pay.. but he woulnt let me.. i thought that was soo sweet... so we bowled.. for and hour.. and laughed and had alot of fun.. his mom drove us back to dan's house and then he opened my door (SOO CUTE!!) me and kell left and she took me home!! it was probly the best brithday EVER!!
    so yea.. thats all i got today!!!! i have to work in like 2 hours.. so im gonna get going.. talk to you all later!!! hehe can you tell im smiling???? :) !!
later,


love ya,
